room_title: Escape room "The Carnival Heist" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: We ended up with a group of folks we didn't know in the VooDoo room and had a blast! Teamwork people! Can't wait to bring the kids.

room_title: Escape room "The Carnival Heist" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: Had a great time! Can't wait to do it again. Would recommend to anyone wanting to do a team building exercise.

room_title: Escape room "The Carnival Heist" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: We had a group of 9 and all family and friends. Great time and even though we didn't escape we will go again to another room. So much fun.

room_title: Escape room "The Carnival Heist" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
